    <title>Multisim保姆级安装教程</title>
    <link href="https://goal75kg.github.io/2021/09/14/Multisim%E4%BF%9D%E5%A7%86%E7%BA%A7%E5%AE%89%E8%A3%85%E6%95%99%E7%A8%8B/"/>
    <id>https://goal75kg.github.io/2021/09/14/Multisim%E4%BF%9D%E5%A7%86%E7%BA%A7%E5%AE%89%E8%A3%85%E6%95%99%E7%A8%8B/</id>
    <published>2021-09-13T23:56:25.000Z</published>
    <updated>2021-09-15T00:21:24.000Z</updated>
    
    <content type="html"><![CDATA[<link rel="stylesheet" class="aplayer-secondary-style-marker" href="\assets\css\APlayer.min.css"><script src="\assets\js\APlayer.min.js" class="aplayer-secondary-script-marker"></script><p>不会安装Multisim？往下看。。。</p><span id="more"></span><ol><li><p>解压压缩包</p><blockquote><p>本文提到的文件在这<a href="http://80kg-images.test.upcdn.net/img/Multisim.rar">点击下载</a></p></blockquote></li><li><p>解压后进入解压后文件夹Multisim<br><img src="https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/gh/Goal75KG/Blog-images/img/Multisim%E5%AE%89%E8%A3%85%E6%95%99%E7%A8%8B/%E8%A7%A3%E5%8E%8B%E5%90%8E.png" alt="解压后"></p></li><li><p>点击进入setup文件夹<br><img src="https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/gh/Goal75KG/Blog-images/img/Multisim%E5%AE%89%E8%A3%85%E6%95%99%E7%A8%8B/%E8%BF%9B%E5%85%A5setup%E6%96%87%E4%BB%B6%E5%A4%B9.png" alt="进入setup文件夹"></p></li><li><p>点击运行setup.exe<br><img src="https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/gh/Goal75KG/Blog-images/img/Multisim%E5%AE%89%E8%A3%85%E6%95%99%E7%A8%8B/%E5%8D%95%E5%87%BBsetup.png" alt="点击运行setup.exe"></p></li><li><p>运行后显示如下界面<br><img src="https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/gh/Goal75KG/Blog-images/img/Multisim%E5%AE%89%E8%A3%85%E6%95%99%E7%A8%8B/%E5%AE%89%E8%A3%85%E7%95%8C%E9%9D%A21.png" alt="安装界面1"></p></li><li><p>点击next<br><img src="https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/gh/Goal75KG/Blog-images/img/Multisim%E5%AE%89%E8%A3%85%E6%95%99%E7%A8%8B/%E5%AE%89%E8%A3%85%E7%95%8C%E9%9D%A22.png" alt="安装界面2"></p></li><li><p>选择 I accept …<br><img src="https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/gh/Goal75KG/Blog-images/img/Multisim%E5%AE%89%E8%A3%85%E6%95%99%E7%A8%8B/%E5%AE%89%E8%A3%85%E7%95%8C%E9%9D%A23.png" alt="安装界面4"></p></li><li><p>username,company name 随意填写（注意不要填写中文）</p><div class="notification is-info"><p>Serial Number 填写<br>F4CG-2551-3040-9001-89768</p></div></li><li><p>选择 I will check …<br><img src="https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/gh/Goal75KG/Blog-images/img/Multisim%E5%AE%89%E8%A3%85%E6%95%99%E7%A8%8B/%E5%AE%89%E8%A3%85%E7%95%8C%E9%9D%A25.png" alt="安装界面5"></p></li><li><p>取消勾选OK….<br><img src="https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/gh/Goal75KG/Blog-images/img/Multisim%E5%AE%89%E8%A3%85%E6%95%99%E7%A8%8B/%E5%AE%89%E8%A3%85%E7%95%8C%E9%9D%A26.png" alt="安装界面6"></p></li><li><p>点击Browse选择你想要安装的路径<a id="demo"></a><br><img src="https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/gh/Goal75KG/Blog-images/img/Multisim%E5%AE%89%E8%A3%85%E6%95%99%E7%A8%8B/%E5%AE%89%E8%A3%85%E7%95%8C%E9%9D%A27.png" alt="安装界面7"></p></li><li><p>弹出错误窗口，点击确定忽略即可<br><img src="https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/gh/Goal75KG/Blog-images/img/Multisim%E5%AE%89%E8%A3%85%E6%95%99%E7%A8%8B/%E5%AE%89%E8%A3%85%E7%95%8C%E9%9D%A29.png" alt="安装界面9"><br><img src="https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/gh/Goal75KG/Blog-images/img/Multisim%E5%AE%89%E8%A3%85%E6%95%99%E7%A8%8B/%E5%AE%89%E8%A3%85%E7%95%8C%E9%9D%A210.png" alt="安装界面10"></p></li><li><p>弹出Adobe软件安装选项，选择是<br><img src="https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/gh/Goal75KG/Blog-images/img/Multisim%E5%AE%89%E8%A3%85%E6%95%99%E7%A8%8B/%E5%AE%89%E8%A3%85%E7%95%8C%E9%9D%A211.png" alt="安装界面11"></p></li><li><p>取消勾选<br><img src="https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/gh/Goal75KG/Blog-images/img/Multisim%E5%AE%89%E8%A3%85%E6%95%99%E7%A8%8B/%E5%AE%89%E8%A3%85%E7%95%8C%E9%9D%A213.png" alt="取消勾选"></p></li><li><p>安装后会弹出文件夹，把里面的快捷方式复制一份到桌面上方便打开<img src="https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/gh/Goal75KG/Blog-images/img/Multisim%E5%AE%89%E8%A3%85%E6%95%99%E7%A8%8B/%E5%AE%89%E8%A3%85%E7%BB%93%E6%9D%9F.png" alt="结束"></p></li><li><p>至此，教程结束 </p></li></ol>]]></content>
    
    
    <summary type="html">&lt;p&gt;不会安装Multisim？往下看。。。&lt;/p&gt;</summary>
    
    
    
